function Start(sWorldName, sLevelAreaName)
	--Setting Portal to next area to visible
	Hydra.SetGameVariableFlag("CAP_Tier2_Frac_CathedralofLight_PortalVisiblity")
	Hydra.MusicOverride("CAP_Tier2_Frac_CathedralofLight", "Music_Boss_PaleFrac_Victory")
end

function Start(nMonstersRemaining, idActorKiller, idActorKilled)

	-- announce the ambush, and make sure the target is valid	
	local idAmbushTarget = DF_KAM_AnnounceAmbush(idActorKiller)
	
	DF_Ambush("Elite", "Knight", idActorKiller)
	DF_Ambush("Ambush", "Knight", idActorKiller)
	
	-- waiting after this one, we're vacuuming the last 10 mobs 
	-- the ambush needs a beat to spawn and get added to the KAM actor group
	Hydra.Wait(0.01)
	
	DF_KAM_CullFarthestMonsters(10, S_KAM_VACUUMED)

end

function Start(flGameTime)

	-- if this is the very first phase, the phase starts before everything is ready, wait a beat 
	-- before spawning markers and checking distances, etc.
	if bInitialized == nil then
		Hydra.Wait(1)
		DF_KAM_Initialize(S_KAM_MARKER)
	end

	-- pull abandoned monsters to a player
	DF_KAM_HeartBeat_Cull(S_KAM_MARKER, S_KAM_VACUUMED)
	
end

function Start(idActorKiller, idActorKilled)	
	------------------------------------------------------
	
	-- First Time Rewards
	
	local tAllPlayers = Hydra.QuestGetParticipants()
	
	for i, idPlayer in ipairs(tAllPlayers) do
		-- Drop the TreasureClass, which contains both "always" and "first time" rewards
		-- The First Time stuff is conditioned by the flag that is set after the drop occurs
		Hydra.TreasureClassDropAtActorForPlayer(idActorKilled, "FirstTimeReward_Capstone_Curator", idPlayer)
		
		-- Set the variable, to mark that this player has recieved a reward
		Hydra.SetPlayerVariableFlag(idPlayer, "FirstTimeReward_Capstone_Curator")
	end
	
	------------------------------------------------------
end

function Start(idActorSummoner, idActorSummoned, sPowerName)
	if Hydra.ActorIsInGroup(idActorSummoned, "DGN_Standard_MoteCarrier") then
		Hydra.ActorRemoveFromGroup(idActorSummoned, "DGN_Standard_MoteCarrier")
	end
end
